text: Horst Möhwald (born 1 June 1938) is a German skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1964 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1938 births Category:Living people Category:People from Trutnov District Category:Sudeten German people Category:German male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of the United Team of Germany Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1964 Winter Olympics
